<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="1698" href="/blog/2014/07/25/pivotal-toronto-meetup-production-grade-applications-with-spring-boot#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
